ine Sirois, Université Laval</p></section><div class="relative hidden aspect-square basis-1/4 sm:aspect-video sm:basis-auto md:block"><img alt="Les mains d&#x27;une personne âgée en train de prendre des médicaments dans un boîtier" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns=&#x27;http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%3E%3Cimage style=&#x27;filter:blur(20px)&#x27; preserveAspectRatio=&#x27;none&#x27; x=&#x27;0&#x27; y=&#x27;0&#x27; height=&#x27;100%25&#x27; width=&#x27;100%25&#x27; href=&#x27;data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPAAALNvUP///yH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==&#x27;/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)" sizes="(min-width: 1466px) 339px, (min-width: 1024px) 243px, (min-width: 640px) 25vw, 25vw" srcSet="https://images.theconversation.com/files/589588/original/file-20240422-16-897dy7.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=256&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=0%2C834%2C4830%2C2415&amp;fit=crop 256w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/589588/original/file-20240422-16-897dy7.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=384&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=0%2C834%2C4830%2C2415&amp;fit=crop 384w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/589588/original/file-20240422-16-897dy7.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=640&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=0%2C834%2C4830%2C2415&amp;fit=crop 640w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/589588/original/file-20240422-16-897dy7.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=768&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=0%2C834%2C4830%2C2415&amp;fit=crop 768w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/589588/original/file-20240422-16-897dy7.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=1024&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=0%2C834%2C4830%2C2415&amp;fit=crop 1024w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/589588/original/file-2024042