bilite-reduite-reste-un-objectif-difficile-a-atteindre-221721" class="group flex w-full gap-2 sm:flex-col-reverse sm:justify-end"><section class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2 sm:basis-auto basis-3/4"><span class="group-hover:text-indigo-600 group-hover:underline"><h5 class="font-bold font-sans-heading text-base leading-5 lg:text-lg lg:leading-6"><span>Malgré les progrès législatifs, la ville accessible aux personnes à mobilité réduite reste un objectif difficile à atteindre</span></h5></span><p class="text-3xs text-gray-600 line-clamp-4">Ron Buliung, University of Toronto</p></section><div class="relative hidden aspect-square basis-1/4 sm:aspect-video sm:basis-auto md:block"><img alt="a man with a cane walks along a sidewalk with textured yellow surfaces" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns=&#x27;http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%3E%3Cimage style=&#x27;filter:blur(20px)&#x27; preserveAspectRatio=&#x27;none&#x27; x=&#x27;0&#x27; y=&#x27;0&#x27; height=&#x27;100%25&#x27; width=&#x27;100%25&#x27; href=&#x27;data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPAAAJJ0W////yH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==&#x27;/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)" sizes="(min-width: 1466px) 339px, (min-width: 1024px) 243px, (min-width: 640px) 25vw, 25vw" srcSet="https://images.theconversation.com/files/570741/original/file-20231218-29-jo501r.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=256&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=0%2C947%2C5755%2C2877&amp;fit=crop 256w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/570741/original/file-20231218-29-jo501r.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=384&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=0%2C947%2C5755%2C2877&amp;fit=crop 384w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/570741/original/file-20231218-29-jo501r.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp